Integrate[(a_.+b_*x_)^m_*Sqrt[c_.+d_*x_]/(Sqrt[e_.+f_*x_]*Sqrt[g_.+h_*x_]),x_] := b*(a+b*x)^(m+1)*Sqrt[c+d*x]*Sqrt[e+f*x]*Sqrt[g+h*x]/((m+1)*(b*e-a*f)*(b*g-a*h)) + 1/(2*(m+1)*(b*e-a*f)*(b*g-a*h))*Integrate[((a+b*x)^(m+1)/(Sqrt[c+d*x]*Sqrt[e+f*x]*Sqrt[g+h*x]))* Simp[2*a*c*f*h*(m+1)-b*(d*e*g+c*(2*m+3)*(f*g+e*h))+2*(a*d*f*h*(m+1)-b*(m+2)*(d*f*g+d*e*h+c*f*h))*x-b*d*f*h*(2*m+5)*x^2,x],x] /;
FreeQ[{a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,m},x] && IntegerQ[2*m] && LeQ[m,-2]

